-- Gupta Group to Start a Daily South African Newspaper, Business Day Says
-- Antony Sguazzin
-- 2010-07-06T05:10:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/gupta-group-to-start-a-daily-south-african-newspaper-business-day-says.html

          
          
             The Gupta Group will fund the start 
up of a daily national newspaper in South Africa to be known as
the New Age in September, Business Day reported, citing Essop 
Pahad, a former cabinet minister who is helping to start the 
publication.  
 The newspaper will be edited by Vuyo Mvoko, 
Johannesburg-based Business Day said, citing Pahad.  
          
          


  


        